text:
Former Labour leader Jeremy Corbyn questions if there is going to be a "rapid increase" in testing to tackle #COVID19.

Health Secretary Matt Hancock says the government has had its "foot on the gas" from the start on testing. 

#PMQs live: https://t.co/rp4wEsnqt2 https://t.co/ojsW49ESD5
